The '''Chatsworth Nature Preserve Coalition''' ('''CNPC''') is an [[advocacy group]] dedicated to protecting and preserving the [[Chatsworth Nature Preserve]] (CNP), located in [[Chatsworth, Los Angeles|Chatsworth]], California, United States. CNPC actions have included writing letters to local governmental agencies and politicians regarding policy decisions affecting the CNP, and participation in the Earth Day Celebration held annually at the CNP. CNPC members include representatives from local [[Conservation movement|conservation group]]s and neighboring residents. The group was founded in 2012.

